Class JavacPluginProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.JavacPluginProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddsToRuleKey, RuleKeyAppendable

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
 @Generated(value={"Immutables.generator","AbstractJavacPluginProperties"})
 @Immutable
public final class JavacPluginProperties
extends Object
    Describes the properties of a plugin to javac, either a Processor or a Plugin. The classpath and input properties in particular can be expensive to compute, so this object should be cached when possible.
